506
00:33:51,767 --> 00:33:53,811
This is about lsabel
and you know it.

507
00:33:54,020 --> 00:33:57,440
She made one mistake, but she's trying.
She's learning.

508
00:33:58,316 --> 00:34:02,528
Slugs have a faster
learning curve. Trees, clams....

509
00:34:03,029 --> 00:34:06,198
Give her some time, will you?
Don't drive her away.

510
00:34:08,659 --> 00:34:10,202
