539
00:36:27,589 --> 00:36:28,506
What?

540
00:36:28,715 --> 00:36:31,092
The clients will be here at 4:30.

541
00:36:31,342 --> 00:36:34,429
I know, so I have to hurry.
Don't worry. I'll be back.

