I mean....

547
00:37:10,339 --> 00:37:12,216
That's something you would do.

548
00:37:15,970 --> 00:37:17,430
To tell you the truth...

549
00:37:20,725 --> 00:37:21,976
...l did.

550
00:37:24,520 --> 00:37:26,897
Your mother had to help
a friend with...

551
00:37:27,648 --> 00:37:28,858
...this emergency.

552
00:37:29,108 --> 00:37:31,318
So she called me to switch days.

553
00:37:31,569 --> 00:37:35,948
But I got caught up at work
and just forgot all about you.

554
00:37:38,159 --> 00:37:39,952
My little chick!

555
00:37:40,911 --> 00:37:44,164
How are you, sweetie? I'm sorry
