You must be starving.

557
00:37:48,043 --> 00:37:49,211
You hungry?

558
00:37:49,420 --> 00:37:50,671
You want a good meal?

559
00:37:51,046 --> 00:37:52,589
How'd you do on your math?

560
00:37:54,300 --> 00:37:55,384
Was it hard?

561
00:38:10,274 --> 00:38:11,108
Who is it?

562
00:38:11,442 --> 00:38:13,944
It's Jackie. May I come in?

563
00:38:14,736 --> 00:38:15,821
Sure.

564
00:38:24,121 --> 00:38:27,624
I have another appointment
this afternoon, and l....

565
00:38:29,167 --> 00:38:30,544
I need somebody...

566
00:38:30,752 --> 00:38:33,130
...to take the children
to the park.

567
00:38:33,338 --> 00:38:35,465
