with my boss.

572
00:38:46,685 --> 00:38:50,021
When I ran out yesterday,
I thought he'd fire me.

573
00:38:50,230 --> 00:38:52,274
I can get somebody else.

574
00:38:52,732 --> 00:38:54,359
Wait. God!

575
00:38:57,028 --> 00:38:59,489
I'll figure something out.
I'll do it.

576
00:39:04,619 --> 00:39:05,662
After-school snack.

577
00:39:05,954 --> 00:39:07,580
Refrigerate, if possible.

578
00:39:08,373 --> 00:39:10,917
Band-Aids, Neosporin, hand-wipes,
Kleenex, Tylenol.

579
00:39:11,167 --> 00:39:13,378
Why not just bring
the whole pharmacy?

580
00:39:14,587 --> 00:39:16,631
Ben likes to be read to.
You know Dr. Seuss?

581
00:39:16,881 --> 00:39:17,882
Not personally.

582
00:39:19,592 --> 00:39:24,639
Do you have a word limit you have to
hit every day, or may I finish?

583
00:39:26,307 --> 00:39:29,394
Here's their schedule, my beeper
number in case of emergency.

584
00:39:29,644 --> 00:39:32,146
If not, I'll see you
at 5 o'clock at the park.

585
00:39:32,397 --> 00:39:35,567
All I ask is that they
are alive when I get there.

586
00:39:36,818 --> 00:39:39,028
Jackie, I wanted to ask you...

587
00:39:39,237 --> 00:39:40,196
...something.

588
00:39:42,532 --> 00:39:46,577
